The WR750RLD has an RP-SMA connector (connected via soldered pigtail), while the WR750RL has an integral antenna (connected via soldered pigtail).
The default IP and credentials are based on the submitted manual in the FCC documents. :The default SSID as shown in the manual is '''Default_11N''' (w/ a 00:0C:43 ['''Ralink'''] OUI containing MAC in the router web UI screenshots)
The FCC test report states that the trade names include PRO-NETS, Speed Com+, and Jet Com.
